              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The fission counting rate in the counters was",
                " calibrated in terms of neutron flux by calculations",
                " based on: the amount of 235-U present as determined",
                " by low geometry alpha-particle assay, published",
                " values for the fission cross section, and",
                " experimentally determined corrections for fission",
                " fragment counting losses due to the thickness and",
                " non-uniformity of the 235-U foil. This calibration",
                " was verified at 14.65 MeV by making an absolute",
                "  measurement using the usual method of counting",
                " the associated alpha-particles from the d-T reaction."
              ]
            }
